{"tid":278323,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅 鈞 滿 FB 晒 坐 Business Class","createTime":"2017-06-10T10:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T12:18:29.000Z","uid":35964,"like":3,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"204416445aecfc9f9ae8c52147e48b5057ffa0eb","tid":278323,"uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:48:08.000Z","msg":"負面新聞多蘿蘿嘅羅鈞滿(Moon)，喺舊年11月無綫台慶嗰日宣佈提前解約，回復自由身嘅Moon，喺香港突然消聲匿跡，好似娛樂圈從未出現過呢個人，之不過此處不留人，自有留人處，阿Moon改投祖國嘅懷抱，拍劇賺人仔！<br />\n<br />\n為咗證明自己有工開，阿Moon好勤力更新微博同fb，睇嚟佢啲生活都好寫意，一時見佢貼啲開工拍劇、商演嘅相，轉個頭又貼下啲旅行睇波相，今日佢又更新近況，佢貼咗啲喺機艙嘅相，留言話：「休息，工作，再工作！橫店見！」不過佢似乎唔係想晒個樣，見佢好寧寧捨捨有一張淨係得護照夾住張登機證嘅相，清楚見到航班編號，機艙級別係商務位，莫非佢借啲意扮不經意咁話俾人知，其實佢出trip做嘢都係坐商務位？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170610/large/1497076127_0de9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170610%2Flarge%2F1497076127_0de9.jpg&h=ffcdf5c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a57d8d7d9592e3cf2a7bfc19f73a5a685fc81c60","tid":278323,"uid":36049,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"好撚似D MK港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a198f45e95311d5fd5415fde7caaa6ccae93f8","tid":278323,"uid":38461,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"去杭州搭business咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd735fb8eb222aa3816774dd233a676887ef2e6b","tid":278323,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"大陸邊個台簽咗佢？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 唔識佢老鼠"},{"pid":"092bcc922c15528b8bee71e771742e12c3d5a3b7","tid":278323,"uid":3567,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20